<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Solana Exchange</title>
  <link href="https://png.pngtree.com/png-clipart/20211208/ourmid/pngtree-3d-rendering-cryptocurrency-solana-black-coin-with-cartoon-style-png-image_4051980.png" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="app-container">
    <header class="app-header">
      <div class="logo-container">
        <img src="https://png.pngtree.com/png-clipart/20211208/ourmid/pngtree-3d-rendering-cryptocurrency-solana-black-coin-with-cartoon-style-png-image_4051980.png" alt="Solana" class="logo">
        <h1>Solana Exchange</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="user-info">
        
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="info-banner">
      <h2>Лучший обменник Solana</h2>
      <p>Обменивайте SOL на USDT и другие токены по выгодному курсу. Низкие комиссии, быстрые транзакции, надежное хранение средств.</p>
    </div>

    <main class="app-content">
      <div class="exchange-card">
        <div class="rate-display">
          <div class="crypto-info">
            <img src="https://cryptologos.cc/logos/solana-sol-logo.png" alt="SOL" class="crypto-icon">
            <span>Solana</span>
          </div>
          <div class="rate-value" id="rate">0.00 USDT</div>
        </div>

        <div class="action-buttons">
          <button class="btn-buy">Buy</button>
          <button class="btn-sell">Sell</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="account-card">
        <h2>Exchange</h2>
        <button class="btn-deposit" id="depositBtn">Deposit</button>
      </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Модальное окно капчи -->
    <div class="modal hidden" id="captchaModal">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <span class="close-modal">&times;</span>
        <h2>Verify you're human</h2>
        <form id="captchaForm">
          <div id="captchaQuestion"></div>
          <input type="text" id="captchaAnswer" placeholder="Your answer" class="input-field" required>
          <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Verify</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>